(670, 'en', 'apps', 'phpfox', '3.0.0beta3', 'setting_enable_api_support', '<title>Enable API Support</title><info>Before developers can start using your site to create Apps you must first enable API support. By enabling this you will allow 3rd party developers the ability to create Apps for your community that they will host and maintain on their own servers. They will get access using a token system that uses OpenSSL. In order for this feature to work your server must have OpenSSL support.</info>', '<title>Enable API Support</title><info>Before developers can start using your site to create Apps you must first enable API support. By enabling this you will allow 3rd party developers the ability to create Apps for your community that they will host and maintain on their own servers. They will get access using a token system that uses OpenSSL. In order for this feature to work your server must have OpenSSL support.</info>', 1316002975),
(671, 'en', 'apps', 'phpfox', '3.0.0beta3', 'setting_openssl_config_path', '<title>OpenSSL Config Path</title><info>If your server does not have a config file for OpenSSL installed you can define the full path to this file here.</info>', '<title>OpenSSL Config Path</title><info>If your server does not have a config file for OpenSSL installed you can define the full path to this file here.</info>', 1316003324),
