(1272, 'en', 'core', 'phpfox', '2.0.7', 'setting_ip_infodb_api_key', '<title>IP InfoDB API Key</title><info>IP InfoDB is a free IP address geolocation tools we use to find useful information about users based on their IP. Enter your free API key, which you can get <a href="http://ipinfodb.com/register.php">here</a>.</info>', '<title>IP InfoDB API Key</title><info>IP InfoDB is a free IP address geolocation tools we use to find useful information about users based on their IP. Enter your free API key, which you can get <a href="http://ipinfodb.com/register.php">here</a>.</info>', 1289988772),
