(2775, 'en', 'user', 'phpfox', '3.1.0rc1', 'setting_shorter_password_reset_routine', '<title>Shorter Password Reset Routine</title><info>If this is enabled when a user clicks on Forgot your password he will receive an email with a link, when clicking on the link he will be shown an input where to change the password. The site will not assign a new password to that user and the previous password will work until it has been reset.</info>', '<title>Shorter Password Reset Routine</title><info>If this is enabled when a user clicks on Forgot your password he will receive an email with a link, when clicking on the link he will be shown an input where to change the password. The site will not assign a new password to that user and the previous password will work until it has been reset.</info>', 1332231623),
