(4850, 'en', 'friend', 'phpfox', '2.0.0rc12', 'setting_enable_friend_suggestion', '<title>Friend Suggestions</title><info>Enable this if you want to suggest friends to your members when they visit their dashboard.\r\n\r\nYou can control the search criteria on what defines a friend to suggest.\r\n\r\nThis feature requires a lot of extra server resources in order to perform such a search. \r\n\r\nEach search result is cached for X minutes (where you can control X).\r\n\r\n<b>Notice:</b> This feature is experimental and is not stable.\r\n</info>', '<title>Friend Suggestions</title><info>Enable this if you want to suggest friends to your members when they visit their dashboard.\r\n\r\nYou can control the search criteria on what defines a friend to suggest.\r\n\r\nThis feature requires a lot of extra server resources in order to perform such a search. \r\n\r\nEach search result is cached for X minutes (where you can control X).\r\n\r\n<b>Notice:</b> This feature is experimental and is not stable.\r\n</info>', 1260554523),
